    test many_connections: Decrease number of connections
    
    On many systems there is a limit of 1024 file descriptors per process by
    default. Recently, for testing purposes, each connection get its
    descriptor duplicated (only in `cfg(test)`). This overflowed the limit.
    This commit decreases the number a bit.

